{"type":"article","id":784,"title":"【RFC-Tracker】","uid":1,"topics":[937],"contents":"RFC 跟踪器<br>\n<br>\n状态说明：<br>\n<br>\n已通过并实施（√√）<br>\n<br>\n已通过但未完成（√）<br>\n<br>\n搁置（≈）：暂时无必要或无条件实行，但又未被否决，将来可在原始 RFC 下重启。<br>\n<br>\n待推进（π）：未决出最终结果，需要更多 comments。<br>\n<br>\n未通过（x）：RFC 被否决，如要实施变更必须提交新的 RFC。<br>\n<br>\nRFC 列表：<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/526\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-001</a>】新品葱采用RFC治理机制 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/1655\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-002</a>】立宪 ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/529\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-003</a>】组党 ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/538\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-004</a>】修改话题详情页 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/1671\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-005</a>】重文章轻问答 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/539\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-006</a>】论坛网游化 ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/577\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-007</a>】删帖封号公示 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/628\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-008</a>】低于一定积分或威望的新用户所发问题和文章放到新人提问栏，而非默认首页显示 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/639\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-009</a>】非站务问题取消“最佳回复”设置 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/654\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-010</a>】优化搜索体验 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/666\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-011</a>】添加wikipedia.org的圖片顯示支持 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/668\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-012</a>】增加直接回复匿名用户的功能 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/733\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-013</a>】增加网站单位时间内的表现指标 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/743\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-014</a>】编辑区增加大标题，乃至多级标题 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/747\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-015</a>】主張屠殺之反人類言論，概予禁止 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/763\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-016</a>】不要再使用8ch.net上传敏感图片 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/769\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-017</a>】签到奖励阶梯制 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/782\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-018</a>】RFC排序及索引 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/788\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-019</a>】提问后加入相关文章和链接 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2352\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-020</a>】创建Steam鉴赏家账户 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/801\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-021</a>】品葱提问建议规范 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/840\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-022</a>】合并繁体和简体标签 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2518\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-023</a>】修改分类（分类可以理解为版块）√√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2519\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-024</a>】修改游戏币规则 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/868\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-025</a>】建议取消私信功能 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/896\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-026</a>】增設用戶單日開題數量上限 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/918\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-027</a>】修改目前提问、赞、踩、提升和下沉机制 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2710\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-028</a>】增加重复提问的关闭机制 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/966\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-029</a>】创建公共编辑账号并锁定密码 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/981\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-030</a>】支持游客发帖回帖 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2904\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-031</a>】停用匿名功能 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/2934\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-032</a>】重启【RFC-002】立宪 的讨论 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/998\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-033</a>】针对捣乱者特点(甚至自动)动态调整发帖回帖等论坛规则和参数 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1026\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-034</a>】取消前台管理员设置最佳回复的权力 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1033\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-035</a>】關於品蔥憲政的建議 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1030\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-036</a>】制定品葱规则 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1034\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-037</a>】用技术化手段降低审查的副作用 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1042\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-038</a>】bookmarklet 一键注册小号(仍须输入验证码) x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1045\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-039</a>】登录用户默认进入「动态」tab x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1046\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-040</a>】7点建议 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1067\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-041</a>】膜乎与新品葱互通 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/3074\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-042</a>】管理员权限与质量改善 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1094\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-043</a>】赞与踩请给个理由 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【RFC-044】不应作为封禁理由的价值观列表 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1140\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-045</a>】针对个人报复性踩的限制 与抛砖引玉 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1171\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-046</a>】不应因为名字碰撞而封禁 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1174\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-047</a>】低威望用户无权使用匿名功能 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1210\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-048</a>】注册页面加入“工作量证明”机制 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1219\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-049</a>】新注册用户观察制度 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1220\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-050</a>】給予管理員一定的刪帖權限 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1245\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-051</a>】根据用户协议，重定向所有人肉相关内容 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1252\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-052</a>】品葱去中心化，发行自己的加密货币 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/3534\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-053</a>】品葱可以增加像旧品葱一样的专栏功能吗？ x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1307\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-054</a>】停止迫害异议人士 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1335\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-055</a>】在用尽每天点赞和反对后，允许使用葱数进行点赞和反对 ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1359\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-056</a>】给用户赞数、葱数添加一个小的随机值 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-057</a>】为回答的评论添加延迟显示功能 ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1377\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-058</a>】成立开发者委员会 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1378\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-059</a>】不应因为名字碰撞而封禁（reopen RFC-046） ≈<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1383\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-060</a>】文章评论也像问题那样形成楼中楼[feature requests] ≈&nbsp; <br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1409\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-061</a>】将Archive加入品葱合法图床 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1468\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-062</a>】在文章和问题页面加入一键Archive按钮 x<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1473\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-063</a>】文章，提问和问题回复 支持YouTube视频链接 √√<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1476\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-064</a>】允许再编辑文章，提问，回复时，修改是否匿名 π<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 【<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/1515\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RFC-065</a>】凡